Attempting `clawq delegate --runner codex --model gpt-5.4 ...` on the current installed binary fails with `unknown option --model`, despite current docs/workspace notes assuming the feature exists. Need to verify whether the source branch lacks the command-bridge wiring on this checkout or whether the running binary is stale; either way the user-facing state is inconsistent and should be tracked.